title: Rockets, Vikings, Browns, Eagles, and the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Rockets, Vikings, Browns, Eagles, and the Blazing 5
description:
Colin explains why the Houston Rockets are in for a long season, why the Minnesota Vikings are not scary at all, why the Cleveland Browns will continue to underachieve, why he can't give up on the Philadelphia Eagles, and his new Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include Danny Kanell, Orlando Scandrick, Shams Charania, Steve Beuerlein, and Jason McIntyre.
